item.description:
Follow the West Side Trail to Semuhenna to Harrington to Summit
Mountain House to Jack Frost to West Rd. to Parking Area
4.5 miles round trip. 3 hours

Directions: From Rt. 140 turn onto Mile Hill Rd.Â  Take next right onto Bolton Rd. , turn left at end onto West Princeton Rd. at fork stay to left, West Princeton Rd. turns into a graded dirt road. follow ~ mile past North Gate. Parking area for trailhead is 1/4 mile after North gate on right. Parking Area holds 6-7 cars. Parking is allowed along road. Trail head is opposite parking area.
